sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Page as Server Component (Page)
  participant Session as getSessionUser()
  participant DB as adminDb() / Firestore

  User->>Page: Request (e.g. /campaigns/xyz/npcs)
  Page->>Session: getSessionUser()
  Session->>Session: Read session cookie
  Session->>Session: verifySessionCookie (Admin Auth)
  Session-->>Page: { uid, email } or null

  alt No user
    Page->>User: redirect(/login)
  else DM reading their own campaign
    Page->>DB: Query by userId == uid (campaigns, npcs, etc.)
    DB-->>Page: Documents
    Page->>User: Render HTML (full data incl. privateNotes)
  else Player reading a campaign
    Page->>DB: Query by playerUserId == uid (players collection)
    DB-->>Page: Player records
    Page->>DB: Get campaign (uid in playerUserIds → allowed by Firestore rules)
    DB-->>Page: Campaign + campaign_npcs / campaign_locations / campaign_factions
    Page->>User: Render HTML (publicInfo only — privateNotes omitted at app layer)
  end
